            <div>
                <head>"Song"</head>
<lg>
    <l>Lovely, dark, and lonely one,</l>
    <l>Bare your bosom to the sun,</l>
    <l>Do not be afraid of light</l>
    <l>You who are a child of night.</l>

    <l>Open wide your arms to life,</l>
    <l>Whirl in the wind of pain and strife,</l>
    <l>Face the wall with the dark closed gate,</l>
    <l>Beat with bare, brown fists</l>
    <l>And wait.</l>
</lg>
    <byline>-Langston Hughes</byline>
        </div>
